{"id": "art-226", "label": "Art. 226", "title": "Art. 226: Ascultarea minorilor şi a majorilor puşi sub ocrotire", "slug": "art-226", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_464771433\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1294\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_464771433\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 226:\nAscultarea minorilor &#351;i a majorilor pu&#351;i sub ocrotire </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1595255675\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1293\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1595255675\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cazul în care, potrivit legii, urmeaz&#259; s&#259;\nfie ascultat un minor, ascultarea se va face în camera de consiliu.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_81884\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1292\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_81884\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În procesele în care urmeaz&#259; s&#259; fie\nascultat&#259; o persoan&#259; care beneficiaz&#259; de consiliere\njudiciar&#259; sau tutel&#259; special&#259;, ascultarea se va face în camera\nde consiliu, dac&#259; instan&#355;a apreciaz&#259; c&#259; este în interesul\nacesteia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1890279112\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1291\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1890279112\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)&#354;inând seama de împrejur&#259;rile procesului,\ninstan&#355;a hot&#259;r&#259;&#351;te dac&#259;, dup&#259; caz,\np&#259;rin&#355;ii, tutorele sau alte persoane vor fi de fa&#355;&#259; la\nascultarea celor prev&#259;zu&#355;i la alin. (1) &#351;i (2).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}